      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, peel your <strong>ginger</strong> (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and chop<strong> </strong>into thin matchsticks</p><p>Top, tail and slice your <strong>radishes</strong> (as finely as you can)</p>",
      "order": 2,
