    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> in a heatproof bowl and stir until the sugar has dissolved</p><p>Add your <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, <strong>ginger matchsticks</strong> and set aside to pickle until serving – this is your<strong> quick-pickled ginger</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
