    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate your<strong> carrot[s]</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
