    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> teriyaki</strong> <strong>prawns</strong> over the<strong> cooked</strong> <strong>rice</strong>, with the <strong>grated carrot</strong>,<strong> quick-pickled ginger</strong>, <strong>sliced radishes </strong>and <strong>mangetout</strong> to the side</p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> over the prawns and garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
